metadata.name: SAVE ME
metadata.description: The artwork seeks to explore the idea of how we can be saved from ourselves and the pain of our experience. And also from external factors. Through its combination of different mediums and the use of digital art, it effectively conveys a sense of hope and possibility that can be found in the depths of despair. The artwork captures the rude emotion of the human condition, making it a captivating and thought provoking piece that is sure to leave a lasting impression.
